src:
Norbert Gombos sa v Bratislave nedostal do štvrťfinále, Klein nestačil na jednotku turnaja
07 Nov 2019, 21:35 by Webnoviny
7.11.2019 (Webnoviny.sk) – Slovenský tenista Norbert Gombos ako nasadená jedenástka nepostúpil do štvrťfinále dvojhry na challengerovom turnaji ATP Peugeot Slovak Open v Bratislave, vo štvrtkovom osemfinále bol nad jeho sily Dennis Novak z Rakúska, s ktorým prehral za 70 minút 5:7, 2:6
V osemfinále neuspel ani Lukáš Klein, keď podľahol najvyššie nasadenému Michailovi Kukuškinovi z Kazachstanu 3:6, 7:6 (4), 4:6.

text:
Norbert Gombos did not make it to the quarterfinals in Bratislava, Klein was not enough for the tournament unit
07 Nov 2019, 21:35 by Webnoviny
7.11.2019 (Webnoviny.sk) - Slovak tennis player Norbert Gombos did not advance to the quarterfinals of the ATP Peugeot Slovak Open in Bratislava in the quarter-finals, in the quarterfinals Dennis Novak from Austria overcame his strength, with which he lost in 70 minutes 5: 7: 2
Lukáš Klein also failed in the eight-final round when he succumbed to the highest seeded Mikhail Kukuškin of Kazakhstan 3: 6, 7: 6 (4), 4: 6.
